tool_input:
{"message": "Hi Iris,

Great question! Yes, you can upgrade your plan at any time, including mid-cycle.

When you upgrade mid-cycle, we use prorated billing:
- You'll only be charged for the portion of the new plan corresponding to the time remaining in your current billing cycle
- For example, if you have 14 days left in your cycle and upgrade from Basic ($10/month) to Pro ($30/month), you'd be charged approximately $9.33 for the remaining 14 days
- Your next full billing cycle will be at the new plan's full price

To upgrade your plan:
1. Go to Account > Subscription
2. Select the plan you want to upgrade to
3. Review the prorated charge
4. Confirm the upgrade

The system will show you exactly what you'll be charged before you confirm. You'll continue to have uninterrupted service throughout the upgrade.

Let me know if you have any other questions!

Best regards,
Customer Support"}
